Your problem is due to the extra parameter `HttpServletRequest` in `logBefore`; which the aspect cannot bind to. If you need an argument from the join point; it is best to inspect it within the aspect. So your `logBefore` method should change from:

```
    @Before(CONTROLLER_EXPRESION)
    public void logBefore(JoinPoint joinPoint, HttpServletRequest request) {

    	// ASPECT LOGIC
    	// ...
    }
```
to this:

```
    @Before(CONTROLLER_EXPRESION)
    public void logBefore(JoinPoint joinPoint) {
    	HttpServletRequest request = (HttpServletRequest)joinPoint.getArgs()[0];

    	// ASPECT LOGIC
    	// ...
    }
```
Hope this helps.

